Acknowledgements
================

This project stands on the shoulders of:

- Filippo Valsorda and the `cryptography` maintainers — Ed25519 primitives.
- Samuel Colvin and the pydantic team — schema validation.
- Tom Christie and encode/* — httpx, rich, click.
- Hynek Schlawack — structlog.
- The dnspython maintainers — async DNS.
- Peter Todd and the OpenTimestamps team — verifiable timestamping.
- The OASIS SARIF working group — interoperable result interchange.

PVNL flag
=========

wimsalabim sails under the Privacy Verzet NL (PVNL) flag. See
https://github.com/WimLee115/Privacy-VerzetNL for the umbrella project.
